{"tid":1319152,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［推上國際］當警隊條例失去威力，警察就變成恐怖分子","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T10:38:51.000Z","uid":5131,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4f1d80154616e56b161b23056a4f147cca3f6340","tid":1319152,"uid":5131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"自從過咗G20 7.1之後 完全睇唔到佢哋有間警隊條例做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n1. 與市民接觸時，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未有委任證展示於適當的位置</span></span><br />\n2. 係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有任何理據底下，封鎖及推進佢哋自稱嘅封鎖線，並非法進入商場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 係企圖驅散人群時，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以非法嘅形式包圍市民，以及於商場進行非法禁錮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">企圖威脅市民人身安全，迫害市民主動作出自衛術，然後再以各種理由進行拘捕。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以上每一個行動， <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行為完全唔符合警隊條例</span></span>， 我哋有理由相信佢哋係一班武裝分子。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即使其身份原本係「警察」，如果唔根據警隊條例進行行動，其性質及身份已經唔屬於警察，而係擁有裝備嘅恐怖份子。</span></span>"},{"pid":"2a67eb8603b2c9abca8802fdeb811ea2f292f982","tid":1319152,"uid":5131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:54:07.000Z","msg":"頭先就咁開咗係吹水台 太快沉 <br />\n<br />\n再推"},{"pid":"a634276f2203c46b8f0ec54e749c283ed58a12ea","tid":1319152,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a>"},{"pid":"9ba136d7be54fc80c4585ca3c186e81145bc099b","tid":1319152,"uid":706,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">請唔好再叫狗/黑警，係懷疑冒警暴徒</span><br />\n<br />\n最低成本既方法，又減低傷亡，和理非都可以幫手<br />\n請幫手推！！<br />\n<br />\n警告你地唔好再屌警察老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://